FILES
------------
  schema.json     JSON Schema (draft-07) for a topic file
  index.json      manifest: topics, paths, counts, notetype mapping
  <slug>.json     one lesson per topic (33 files)
  html/<slug>.html  self-contained Tufte-clean review page per topic
  html/index.html   hub linking every topic page
  build.py        authoring source of truth; regenerates all of the above
  README          this file

REGENERATE
------------
  cd gmatwiz/lessons && python3 build.py
  (writes only inside gmatwiz/lessons/; touches no repo source.)

CITATIONS
------------
Each lesson links a high-trust primary source (OpenStax open textbooks,
Khan Academy, and mba.com for exam structure). See each topic's HTML
'Primary source' box and the citations[] array in its JSON.
